vote.title: A resolution authorizing (1) a joint elections agreement and election services contract between the City of Dallas, Dallas County, and various other jurisdictions within Dallas County, for the conduct of a special election to be held Tuesday, November 5, 2024, in an amount not to exceed $2,714,577.64; and (2) advertising in connection with the Tuesday, November 5, 2024 Special Election, in an amount not to exceed $150,000.00 - Total not to exceed $2,864,577.64 - Financing:  General Fund
